latestIgtvVideos.caption:
PAC launched 5 new skincare products in #SkinSeptember 

1. Travel With Me Charcoal Makeup Remover Wipes

These wipes help restore clean skin from oily and combination skin and unclog congested pores. Travel with me charcoal wipes soothe and refresh your skin, while vitamin E acts as an antioxidant

2. Hydro Fuse Eye Cream

Infuse the skin around your eyes with the power of H2o, Shea Butter, Niacinamide and Macadamia oil. Before you cover those imperfections with concealers and primers show them some love with a hydrating eye cream.

3. Total Clean Cleansing Balm

Total Cleansing Balm is a luxurious makeup remover that nourishes as it cleans. A lightweight cleansing balm that lovingly dissolves all the long stay makeup over your eyes and face and lips while calming the skin at the same time.

4. Rise & Glow Tonic Mist

It covers the skin pores, creating a smoothening effect and gives instant radiance.

5. Spotlight Primer

Perfect under makeup or alone, the formula creates a smooth canvas for makeup application and keeps makeup fresh throughout the day

Visited Shirdi for the first time in my life… but somehow, it didn’t feel like the first. My father has been a Sai Baba devotee since his childhood — I’ve grown up hearing stories, prayers, and Om Sai Ram echoing through our home. 🙏

Walking into the temple, I felt an unexpected wave of emotion… like I was finally meeting someone who had been silently guiding us all along.  It was surreal and the fact that I get to do such things with my husband makes it even more special.

Next on my mission, is taking my parents along who still haven’t stepped their foot in this holy city 🤞🏼
